subsection.content:
a legal mortgage or debenture incorporating leasehold property or
                        interests therein, executed pursuant to an agreement for a mortgage or
                        debenture already charged for under this Part;

the approval of the form of a second or subsequent mortgage or
                        debenture incorporating leasehold property or interests therein on behalf of
                        a mortgagee or debenture holder having priority;

all deeds or agreements for an extension of time for repayment of a
                        mortgage or debenture unless such extension is contained in or is incidental
                        to a further charge;

a debenture not incorporating leasehold property or interests therein,
                        executed pursuant to an agreement for a debenture already charged for under
                        this Part;

the approval of the form of a second or subsequent debenture not
                        incorporating leasehold property or interests therein on behalf of a
                        debenture holder having priority;
